{"tid":663460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果手機未標註台北屬中國 中媒：應給公眾交代","createTime":"2018-05-13T10:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T10:45:24.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5943d0e74c99326b2dc89c97ee4ec1969ed228","tid":663460,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"中國日前向美國航空公司要求台灣不應列為國家引發世界關注。而中媒《看看新聞》近日卻又指出，有蘋果手機用戶投訴，手機內的「世界時鐘」在大部分的城市後方都會括弧所屬國家，但他發現，不僅澳門未標示為中國，台北也完全沒有標示。對此，該媒體也在報導中表示，蘋果公司應給公眾一個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n據《看看新聞》指出，一名蘋果手機用戶賀先生指出，在手機內「世界時鐘」的應用程式中，澳門被單獨設置成一個國家，而台北的後方則也是沒有標註「中國」兩個字，並表示，「香港、澳門與台北」這3個大城市標示竟有所不同，讓他十分不解。<br />\n<br />\n此外他也發現，在iOS 10.2系統中，香港的後面也未標示隸屬於中國，但最新的iOS 11.3系統中，卻又標示上「中國」。他認為，既然香港有了改動，為何澳門和台北沒有相應更改？而該則報導也在文末指出，對於蘋果這麼一家大公司來說，想要在軟件上更改添加內容並非難事，希望蘋果公司能針對此事，給公眾一個交代。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-05-11/656/20180511004767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-05-11%2F656%2F20180511004767.jpg&h=41cb6ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2423936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2423936&d=IsixMzkrNcrT8daeKO7fVb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=e4d17baa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2423936&h=e16b0a49\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2423936</a>"},{"pid":"ae332e1f6ca35f207ed40fe3ee2da65de5f0e438","tid":663460,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:21:28.000Z","msg":"支那蘋果公司客服人員回應稱，他們沒有權限更改，因蘋果系統是由美國那邊升級。<br />\n<br />\n除了蘋果手機，支那的華為手機世界時鐘設置，「香港」、「澳門」後面，都有括號中國予以備註，但「台北」後面，同樣沒有標註中國。至於小米手機，其世界時鐘內的所有城市都沒有標註所屬國家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180512/bkncn-20180512114357330-0512_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180512%2Fbkncn-20180512114357330-0512_05011_001.html&d=IsixMzkrNcrT8daeKO7fVb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=cb821346\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180512/bkncn-20180512114357330-0512_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"147dc56c429adbcf72942e09ceee46739dfa6c55","tid":663460,"uid":106633,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"台北（中華民國）"},{"pid":"ca1ce63908fe56f072f8bf33e492b4840fca93fb","tid":663460,"uid":54264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:36:30.000Z","msg":"笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f215c4d140e306d02aa1e3d2a561bf248b2b3d5a","tid":663460,"uid":87723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"點解支那唔抵制蘋果嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a71668f58d63ac4c13e7d70a73268a0ff87b3d7","tid":663460,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:45:24.000Z","msg":"罷買蘋果啦屌你老母！<br />\n咁都忍得仲話自己愛國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}